    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>13th-level Soulknife feature</i></p><p>You can weave a veil of psychic static to mask yourself. As an action, you can magically become &amp;Reference[condition=invisible], along with anything you are wearing or carrying, for 1 hour or until you dismiss this effect (no action required). This invisibility ends early immediately after you deal damage to a creature or you force a creature to make a saving throw.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a Psionic Energy die to use this feature again.</p></div>",
